Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第62话 高深莫测的阿椿咒术
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.87,0:03:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:47.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么抵抗都是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.01,0:03:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖的\N成为妖怪的饵食吧  犬夜叉!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要不用铁碎牙就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.15,0:04:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种杂碎妖怪  单手就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.02,0:04:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴硬的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.09,0:04:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞刃血爪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.91,0:04:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.31,0:04:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要忘了  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.69,0:04:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇的性命还在我的手上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:48.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  该怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.67,0:04:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.67,0:04:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题…没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.38,0:05:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师  去帮助犬夜叉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:04.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样戈薇会撑不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…椿不论犬夜叉赢或输
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.26,0:05:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都打算咒杀戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  非得切断椿的咒术不可
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒椿  或打倒咒术媒介的式神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.47,0:05:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇在倒下去之前曾说过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:27.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被不知名的东西咬了一口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:31.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  那可能就是黑巫女的式神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.15,0:05:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该就是那条蛇没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.72,0:05:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  麻烦你掩护我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.72,0:05:37.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.99,0:05:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破魔符吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.24,0:05:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别做无谓的挣扎了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢!我的咒术是不会破解的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不清楚情况的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.32,0:06:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抵抗只会延长戈薇的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:26.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说到不如
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:30.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就送戈薇上路算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  振作点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚…我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:48.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上就起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.56,0:06:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么声音?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.23,0:06:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吵…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:06:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.30,0:06:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪…谁在叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.57,0:07:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  快点起床
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.31,0:07:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.08,0:07:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底想睡到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.32,0:07:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.82,0:07:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么会在这边的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.76,0:07:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你睡迷糊了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:29.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要吃早餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.11,0:07:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.11,0:07:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连早安都不会说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.85,0:07:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.05,0:07:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.12,0:07:52.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是什么时候回到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.35,0:07:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:55.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有去过什么地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.92,0:07:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.63,0:07:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那边的世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五百年前过去的世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:05.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是进入隐密的井里面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.23,0:08:08.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来到有很多妖怪的战国时代
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你进去过那口井里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.67,0:08:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是已经来回好几次了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连犬夜叉都有来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.15,0:08:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们连犬夜叉都忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.18,0:08:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷  你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.45,0:08:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里长着狗耳朵的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.26,0:08:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐  今天向学校请假比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.83,0:08:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是睡迷糊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:52.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.35,0:08:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐  快迟到了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.35,0:08:58.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.79,0:09:02.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前的事情  全部都是梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.09,0:09:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点精神都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.20,0:09:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在烦恼什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.10,0:09:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是跟男朋友处的不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了!你们还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.71,0:09:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个男生的事情对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:23.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  果然不是在作梦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,B班的北条同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.18,0:09:29.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.72,0:09:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是爱吃醋又粗鲁任性的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.35,0:09:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇你脚踏两条船吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.36,0:09:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.83,0:09:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇真有精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.74,0:09:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然还搞不懂状况
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.37,0:09:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是突然回到原来的生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.21,0:09:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日暮同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:09:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:09:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着念下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.02,0:10:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考试快到了  别再发呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考试
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错…我必须要准备考试
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.10,0:10:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我原本的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是我的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日暮同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.64,0:10:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北条同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.51,0:10:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.12,0:10:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我听说\N日暮同学没什么精神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个对身体很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,踩踩看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.75,0:10:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.79,0:10:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是哪里不太对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得这样下去不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.50,0:10:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要很多小孩呢\N讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.28,0:11:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶  买四魂之玉给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:06.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.05,0:11:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.55,0:11:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起这个四魂之玉的由来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要从战国时代…\N走吧  奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.58,0:11:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小蚋  我觉得自己怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:48.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,许许多多的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:51.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在脑海里转来转去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.09,0:11:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好像有一件非做不可的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要回忆起来的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:12.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愈来愈模糊了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.62,0:12:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然一直有一种不可以再这样下去的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但到底是什么事非做不可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时感受到的脖子的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也渐渐的习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.54,0:12:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,思绪也变的无法止息了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.69,0:12:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.02,0:12:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.26,0:12:59.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要焦急
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.16,0:13:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么觉得不安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了  日暮同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  抱歉  北条同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.17,0:13:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日暮同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.41,0:13:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总算来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.58,0:13:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要试试看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.56,0:13:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为了这个而来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  那个标靶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好的瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.10,0:13:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,0:13:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,架式不错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.21,0:13:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.08,0:13:52.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你的集中力不够
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问…请问你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.89,0:14:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.23,0:14:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.40,0:14:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉又会丧命的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.47,0:14:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.14,0:14:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.61,0:14:28.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬…犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.25,0:14:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还无法离开这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.63,0:14:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:45.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:47.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是说这个的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界是你的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己决定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.15,0:14:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.78,0:14:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.53,0:15:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.34,0:15:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么还能动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的集中力不够吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.19,0:15:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你已经能耐住咒缚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:47.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谣传你是桔梗转世
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.00,0:15:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎不全是唬人的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.83,0:15:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是真正的桔梗  刚才那一箭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该能确实的命中我才对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.01,0:16:00.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底你不过是桔梗的赝品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.21,0:16:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这人真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.21,0:16:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.35,0:16:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是其他人!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.74,0:16:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢的家伙  这么急着找死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.52,0:16:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.74,0:17:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样下去  戈薇会支持不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  能再稍微撑一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.45,0:17:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会努力试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.76,0:17:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那两人大卸八块
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.60,0:17:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会让你被杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我闪开  杂碎!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散魂铁爪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:48.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了  椿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.85,0:17:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.97,0:18:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死心吧  椿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.97,0:18:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为这样就能切断咒术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.51,0:18:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.48,0:18:16.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诅咒的效力还存在着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.69,0:18:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是杀了式神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你们几个也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.74,0:18:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有妖怪在她的体内吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.56,0:19:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云母  留在戈薇的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.96,0:19:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,式神…该不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.09,0:19:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕!这些妖怪全都是诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在才发现太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.83,0:19:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,式神!咬断那女人的脖子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.33,0:19:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺取四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.83,0:19:45.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.87,0:19:55.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.01,0:19:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:20:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.82,0:20:07.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.26,0:20:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会输给你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.87,0:20:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将式神打回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.34,0:20:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是咒术反噬!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:26.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和桔梗一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.21,0:20:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那个时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会被这小丫头给…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.80,0:20:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉被净化了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.25,0:21:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碎片取出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.49,0:21:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.19,0:21:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她要逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.99,0:21:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想跑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.69,0:21:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住  臭家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.67,0:21:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.68,0:21:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶…逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.89,0:21:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.52,0:21:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.80,0:21:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.77,0:22:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂碎片就那样给她?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.80,0:22:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么  马上就能取回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.54,0:22:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.81,0:22:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.64,0:22:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给黑巫女一个雪耻的机会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.78,0:22:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还蛮体贴的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.96,0:22:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耗尽力量了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.16,0:22:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因为那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.16,0:22:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饲养的妖怪统统死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.40,0:22:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明就只差一步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.90,0:22:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是只要有这颗四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.21,0:22:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能让我的力量更加强大
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.24,0:22:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次我一定会打倒他们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.75,0:22:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好觉悟吧  犬夜叉  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.46,0:22:59.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇十分疲倦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.23,0:23:00.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是不得已的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.00,0:23:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她一直和咒术抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.73,0:23:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.10,0:23:08.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.87,0:23:11.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我在一起老是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.77,0:23:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.44,0:23:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我喜欢和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.78,0:23:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.65,0:24:56.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.75,0:23:40.35,ED,,0,0,0,,究竟要流多少泪{\fad(500,0)}
